Uses of Package
com.thesonofthom.maps

  • Packages that use com.thesonofthom.maps 
    Package Description
    com.thesonofthom.maps  
  • Classes in com.thesonofthom.maps used by com.thesonofthom.maps 
    Class and Description
    BmpHeaderMap
    Map to easily parse the BMP file format used by Windows.
    BmpHeaderMap.BitfieldMask
    Structure of the Bitfield Mask that optionally following a bmp that contians a BITMAPINFOHEADER DIB Header.
    BmpHeaderMap.BitmapFileHeader
    Map to parse the header of a potential BMP file to determine if it is, in fact, a bitmap
    BmpHeaderMap.BitmapInfoHeader
    Same as the BITMAPINFOHEADER struct.
    BmpHeaderMap.BitmapV3InfoHeader
    Same as the BITMAPV3INFOHEADER struct.
    BmpHeaderMap.BitmapV4Header
    Same as the BITMAPV4HEADER struct.
    BmpHeaderMap.CieXYZ
    Same as the CIEXYZ struct.
    BmpHeaderMap.CieXYZTriple
    Same as the CIEXYZTRIPLE struct.
    BmpHeaderMap.ColorSpaceType
    Possible values for the ColorSpace field in the BITMAPV4HEADER
    BmpHeaderMap.CompressionType
    Possible values for the Compression field in the BITMAPINFOHEADER
    BmpHeaderMap.DIBHeader
    Base class for all different DIB Header types.
    BmpHeaderMap.DIBHeaderSize
    The Size field in the DIB Header determines what data will follow it BITMAPV3INFOHEADER - BITMAPV5INFOHEADER simply expand upon the previous header.
    BmpHeaderMap.RenderingIntent
    Possible values for the Intent field in the BITMAPV5HEADER
    BmpHeaderMap.RGBQuad
    Same as the RGBQUAD struct.
    PngFileMap
    Map to easily parse the PNG file format.
    PngFileMap.BKGDChunkData
    Data section for "bKGD" chunks.
    PngFileMap.Chunk
    Class for parsing all Chunk types besides IHDR
    PngFileMap.ChunkData
    Abstract class to represent the data section of each Chunk
    PngFileMap.ColorTypeEnum
    Enum to represent the possible values of the ColorType field in the "IHDR" chunk.
    PngFileMap.IHDRChunk
    the IHDR chunk will always appear immediately after the standard PNG header
    PngFileMap.MonthEnum
    Enum to parse the Month field in "tIME" chunk.
    PngFileMap.PLTEChunkData.PLTEChunkEntry
    For each entry in the array in a "PLTE" chunk
    PngFileMap.PngHeader
    Map to parse the header of a potential PNG file to determine if it is, in fact, a PNG file
    PngFileMap.SBITChunkData
    Data section for "sBIT" chunks.
    PngFileMap.SBITChunkDataGrayscale
    Data section for "sBit" chunks when the ColorType is Greyscale
    PngFileMap.SBITChunkDataTruecolorIndexed
    Data section for "sBit" chunks when the ColorType is TrueColor or Indexed_color
    PngFileMap.SRGBRenderingIntent
    Enum to represent the possible values of the RenderingIntent field of the "sRGB" chunk
    PngFileMap.TRNSChunkData
    Data section for "tRNS" chunks.
    PngFileMap.UnitSpecifierEnum
    Enum to represent the possible values of the UnitSpecifier field in the "pHYs" chunk
    WinExeFileHeaderMap
    Map to easily parse the header of standard Windows Executable files (.exe, .dll, etc).
    WinExeFileHeaderMap.DOSHeaderMap
    Map to parse the "DOS Header" section of the executable file header.
    WinExeFileHeaderMap.MachineId
    Enum to represent the various possible values in the Machine variable in COFFHeaderMap
    WinExeFileHeaderMap.PEHeaderMap
    Map to parse the "PE Header" section of the executable file header.
    WinExeFileHeaderMap.PEHeaderMap.COFFHeaderMap
    Map to Parse the "COFF Header" section of the executable file header The COFF header is present in both COFF object files (before they are linked) and in PE files where it is known as the "File header".
    WinExeFileHeaderMap.PEHeaderMap.COFFHeaderMap.COFFHeaderCharacteristics
    Map to define the individual bits that represents the Characteristics field in the COFF Header
    WinExeFileHeaderMap.PEHeaderMap.DataDirectory
    Class to parse the individual fields in the DataDirectory array inside the PE Optional Header Same as the IMAGE_DATA_DIRECTORY struct in WinNT.h
    WinExeFileHeaderMap.PEHeaderMap.DLLCharacteristics
    Map to define the individual bits that represents the DLLCharacteristics field in the PE Optional Header
    WinExeFileHeaderMap.PEHeaderMap.PEOptionalHeader
    Map to parse the "PE Optional Header" in the header.
    WinExeFileHeaderMap.PEOptionalHeaderMagic
    Enum to represent the various possible values in the Magic variable in PEOptionalHeader
    WinExeFileHeaderMap.SubsystemId
    Enum to represent the various possible values in the Subsystem variable in PEOptionalHeader
